# Canonical host enforcement (Netlify / Cloudflare Pages compatible)
# 1) www -> non-www (301)
https://www.yellodae.com/*    https://yellodae.com/:splat    301!
http://www.yellodae.com/*     https://yellodae.com/:splat    301!

# 2) http -> https on apex
http://yellodae.com/*         https://yellodae.com/:splat    301!

# 3) SPA fallback — every other path serves index.html (no redirect chain)
/*    /index.html    200
